• SSL               contains X.509 certificates, secret key and secret DH params.
• nginx.conf        NGINX configuration.
• space.service     systemd service unit file for the CoreOS host system.
• Dockerfile        defines build process for the space machine.
• Flightplan.coffee defines methods to control the machine with the fly command.
• Makefile          defines tasks to generate various SSL files.
• package.json      defines package dependencies.
• README            this file.

0 git clone git@github.com:pinkturtle/space.git
1 npm install ... to get dependencies.
2 make ... to generate SSL files.
3 fly setup:space
4 fly start:space
